<H3><I>INTRODUCTION</I></H3>
</CENTER>

A private network is any form of inter-organizational
communications system where the  customer has control of the usage
of the telecommunications channels.   There are voice networks,
data networks, video networks, integrated networks, dedicated
networks,  virtual networks,>
